## Rules (Auto-Applied)

All rules in `.cursor/rules/core/` with `alwaysApply: true` are automatically applied:

- `agent-identification.mdc` - Banner format (CRITICAL)
- `approval-gates.mdc` - Human approval at phase gates
- `code-quality.mdc` - Code quality standards
- `env-loading.mdc` - Load environment variables
- `execution.mdc` - Execution rules
- `next-step-guidance.mdc` - Show available actions
- `safe-refactoring.mdc` - Review all usages before changing code
- `smart-commenting.mdc` - Comment standards (WHY not WHAT)
- `tdd-approach.mdc` - TDD methodology
- `tech-spec-requirement.mdc` - TECH_SPEC_AI.md creation (MANDATORY)
- `workflow-naming.mdc` - File naming conventions

